Note on source material:

The persona and place files in this folder are original works by Kai Schlüter,
built on the historical tradition of the Sønderjysk kaffebord.

The primary historical source is:
  Inge Adriansen — Det sønderjyske kaffebord (Grænseforeningens Årbog, 1998)

Siegfried Lenz (1926–2014) appears in this world as a historical figure —
his documented presence at Als and his interest in the tradition —
not as a persona derived from his literary work.
Lenz's writing remains under copyright until approximately 2084.
No intellectual property in Lenz's writing is claimed.

The KAI HACKS architecture — its methods, templates, and structural elements —
is the original contribution claimed under this license.

